==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pedicellaria
<hw>Ped`i*cel*la"ri*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;
<plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Pedicellari⟦ae⟧</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu>
<ety>[NL. See <er>Pedicel</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A
peculiar forcepslike organ which occurs in large numbers upon starfishes
and echini. Those of starfishes have two movable jaws, or blades, and
are usually nearly, or quite, sessile; those of echini usually have
three jaws and a pedicel. See <xex>Illustration</xex> in
Appendix.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pedicellate</ent>⟦br⟧
